<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-03-25T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-03-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="398" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d398">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Taylor</persName>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-03-25"><hi rend="italic">March 25,
                                1895</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Inform minister foreign affairs that President appreciates his generous
                            assurances and the great responsibilities he has suddenly assumed, and
                            does not permit himself to doubt that <hi rend="italic">Alliança</hi>
                            incident will be satisfactorily adjusted in due time without disturbance
                            of the friendly relations between the two Governments.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Gresham.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>